  "title": "Understanding Scales",
  "lessonText": "Scales are the building blocks of music, essential for melody and harmony.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- A scale is a series of notes in a specific order.\n- The most common scale is the major scale.\n- Scales can be ascending or descending.\n- Each scale has a unique pattern of whole and half steps.\n- Understanding scales helps in improvisation and composition."
  }
}
